  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To explore the efficacy, safety and tolerability of STX209 (arbaclofen) administered for the
      treatment of social withdrawal in subjects with autism spectrum disorders
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
